      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i feel like maybe we're overreacting? it's just travel fatigue, right? he's 72 so he's always a bit slow after a big trip. plus he's been drinking a little bit of wine to relax. u sure we shouldn't just let him take a nap and see if he's better in the morning? i dont want to drag him to an er if it's just jet lag.",
